title: DEAD OR ALIVEÂ® 5 Last Round [1.04 Repack, +DLCs, Steamworks]
description:
All original game files, with REVOLT Steamworks patch (steam_api.dll) to allow online play with others using the same patch.

Simply extract the 7z anywhere and use game.exe to launch the game. Make sure Steam is running and logged in.

To change display settings, edit DOA5LR.ini and use game.bat to launch the game. Follow the same format, and use the guide below:

-Screen settings:
.WINDOW
.FULL

-Res:
.1024x768
.1280x720
.1280x800
.1366x768
.1600x900
.1680x1050
.1920x1080
.3840x2160

-Shadow:
.ENABLE
.DISABLE

-Shadow Res:
.1024x1024
.2048x2048
.4096x4096

See you in game ;)
